text: Hennie Kenkhuis (19 April 1952 - 17 February 2021) was a Dutch politician. He was alderman for GroenLinks / The Greens from October 2007 to April 2010 in the Dutch city of Zwolle.Afscheid van Kenkhuis Kenkhuis was born in Zenderen (Borne) and died in Zwolle at the age of 68. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Aldermen of the Netherlands Category:GreenLeft politicians Category:Politicians from Overijssel
title: Hennie Kenkhuis
